detail.name: Son Gohan : Childhood
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Place this card in a Battle Area into its owner's Drop : If your Leader is <Son Gohan : Childhood> and you have <Android 16> in your Drop, play up to 1 <Son Gohan : Childhood> with a cost of 6 or 7 from your hand in Rest Mode.

detail.name: 孫悟飯：少年期
